===============================

Maya and Nuke python tools.

===============================

REQUIREMENTS:
- NukeX.X and MayaX installed
- python2.7 installed in c:/python27
- sublime text editor to be able to build and install

INSTALL:
- clone dmptools: git clone git://github.com/michael-ha/dmptools.git
- open Sublime Text
- project > open > dmptools.sublime-project
- open dmptools/Install.py
- tools > build system > dmptools
- tools > build

RESULT:
In Maya you should new see a new shelf
In Nuke you should now see a new toolbar